{"tid":2387093,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美心麵包有原隻壁虎 美心承認過失罰款9000元","createTime":"2021-01-30T05:14:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T07:39:58.000Z","uid":217049,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c9a1916113a295b3a8f4b7a2b60aa2da9ff8b862","tid":2387093,"uid":217049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T05:14:13.000Z","msg":"一名男子於2019年10月在美心餅店購買肉鬆紫菜麻糬包，發現包內有一條原隻壁虎，隨即向餅店投訴及向政府報案。美心在庭上承認「食物的品質與購買人所要求者不符」罪。裁判官梁雅忻形容事件「有啲誇張」，並指店舖有責任確保外來昆蟲不會進入食物，因而處以9000港元罰款。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HEdywcGapCfnjO9kcxhJzq81J5s=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HTLLBQ3FNFFW5G7A2XA5S3GAIE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHEdywcGapCfnjO9kcxhJzq81J5s%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHTLLBQ3FNFFW5G7A2XA5S3GAIE.jpg&h=d39e880d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n案件編號：TMS 1943/2020"},{"pid":"d8b8b711be58ea0f49253d78d1154fc0d83f0676","tid":2387093,"uid":133641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T05:15:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe37f5ee843acfc5cfeaa766b7605743e7ec303","tid":2387093,"uid":66049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T05:17:34.000Z","msg":"仲買美心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c920dcf1485dde2dbd7da9873dffe30bce273a8","tid":2387093,"uid":36157,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T05:18:38.000Z","msg":"放棄年輕人<br />\n死老野一早就話賺撚左啦"},{"pid":"611917b9709306fe4d14f3794bc67e4968fe4108","tid":2387093,"uid":85586,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T05:19:21.000Z","msg":"美心：九千蚊當跌畀你班乞兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d